I'm really glad to be joined here by Will Landau. He's not quite on stage, but will be.

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:21.120
Will Landau is the author of Target and also the author of Crew, which extends Mirai to high

00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:27.840
performance computing. We'd also like to think that we're joined in spirit at least by this guy,

00:00:28.559 --> 00:00:34.560
Zhou Cheng, creator of Shiny. You'll notice he's not on stage because he's at this moment on

